1. Baskı
The English
https://imageserver.kitapyurdu.com/select.php?imageid=1199403&width=500&isWatermarked=true
2007-01-01
 58,96
In The English Jeremy Paxman sets out to find about the English. Not the British overall, not the Scots, not the Irish or Welsh, but the English. Why do they seem so unsure of who they are?Jeremy Paxman is to many the embodiment of Englishness yet even he is sometimes forced to ask: who or what exactly are the English? And in setting about addressing this most vexing of questions, Paxman discovers answers to a few others.
320
 Jeremy Paxman
